  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Campa&#xF1;a Defensores Colombia:&quot;Somos como T&#xFA;&quot; PAS-PI 2018</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN"># SomosComoT&amp;uacute;, national campaign for the legitimacy of the work of defense of human rights in Colombia, is a proposal that aims to articulate a set of communication and social pedagogy actions, to contribute with the awareness of social actors and institutions about the situation of leaders and social leaders, rural human rights defenders. In the idea of &#x200B;&#x200B;Encouraging a favorable narrative towards human rights defenders to counteract the stigmatization to which they are subjected for their work, especially by some local authorities.
The Campaign is inaugurated this year 2018 to make visible the processes of defense of Magdalena Medio rights through art and memory processes accompanied by PAS-PI and other partner organizations, in order to first raise awareness about the legitimacy of the processes of defense that are advanced in the rural areas of the Magdalena Medio region and generate empathy in the people we are going to reach in the campaign, telling who are the people being attacked from a human perspective and with this we promote different thoughts and positive on HRDs.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project mainly contributes to results within Empowerment of human rights defenders. Results will be reported later in the Global Civsam grant period 2016-2020</narrative>
  </description>
